lenders.name: Network
lenders.occupational_info: Network for Good offers donation pages, peer-to-peer fundraising campaigns & donor management software to help your nonprofit get more donations with less effort. Network for Good powers more digital giving than any other platform. We provide nonprofits, corporations, and software developers with simple solutions to power the good they do with supporters, employees, and consumers. Here's how it works: If you’re a nonprofit, we offer a suite of services that helps you raise money and reach more donors online – plus the coaching that will make you an online fundraising superstar. If you’re a company, we can enable your employees or customers to give to any charity on your site, social networks or mobile devices. We can also set up a micro-site for your organization or power your rewards programs with charity gift cards. If you’re a software developer creating innovative ways to give, our platform can process, track, and distribute donations to any charity. And if you’re a donor, we make it easy to support your favorite charities – choose from any of over 1 million!

lenders.name: Eddy Gicheru
lenders.loan_because: We run an organization called Peace for Africa and Economic Development (PAD) (www.padinst.org) that works on youth education, entrepreneurship and empowerment. PAD helps the youth to start their own individual or group income-generating projects. Since PAD monitors, evaluates and advise on their capacity building, we are able to pick a sustainable or performing project from the myriad of youths we are working with.
